{"html": [{"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">AUTORIZA EMISOR ELECTR&#xD3;NICO</div></div>", "i": 9293812}, {"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Extracto de resoluci&#xF3;n exenta del Servicio de Impuestos Internos N&#xBA; 94, del 31 de agosto de 2012, que autoriza a contribuyentes como emisores electr&#xF3;nicos.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se autoriza como emisor de documentos tributarios electr&#xF3;nicos a contribuyentes RUT 76.187.958-8, RUT 76.670.250-3, RUT 22.412.940-8, RUT 76.213.558-2, RUT 76.214.556-1, RUT 76.063.554-5, RUT 76.219.537-2, RUT 73.056.100-8, RUT 82.962.800-7, RUT 96.856.360-2, RUT 76.177.428-K, RUT 77.853.060-0, RUT 76.171.754-5, RUT 17.677.081-3, RUT 76.141.853-K, RUT 96.793.680-4, RUT 84.177.300-4, RUT 77.345.310-1, RUT 79.523.490-K, RUT 76.217.559-2, RUT 76.058.391-K, RUT 78.610.160-3, RUT 77.886.160-7, RUT 76.148.281-5, RUT 76.101.267-3, RUT 78.088.970-5, RUT 77.307.280-9, RUT 76.096.399-2, RUT 76.592.530-4, RUT 76.149.673-5, RUT 76.163.495-K, RUT 76.751.580-4, RUT 76.211.701-0, RUT 96.930.480-5, RUT 83.162.400-0, RUT 07.699.583-4, RUT 77.580.000-3, RUT 76.696.440-0, RUT 76.627.460-9, RUT 76.216.611-9, RUT 85.120.600-0, RUT 77.376.100-0, RUT 76.194.922-5, RUT 72.548.600-6, RUT 76.264.960-8, RUT 76.145.769-1, RUT 76.051.550-7, RUT 76.078.281-5, RUT 94.050.000-1, RUT 77.839.500-2, RUT 76.213.960-K, RUT 76.836.750-7, RUT 93.217.000-0, RUT 76.758.790-2, RUT 77.727.750-2, RUT 76.218.343-9, RUT 76.189.795-0, RUT 77.685.240-6, RUT 78.518.780-6, RUT 76.078.278-5, RUT 96.846.370-5, RUT 76.455.620-8, RUT 76.089.207-6, RUT 76.077.177-5, RUT 11.473.539-6, RUT 76.048.071-1, RUT 96.931.150-K, RUT 77.103.920-0, RUT 76.206.655-6, RUT 76.218.021-9, RUT 13.683.745-1, RUT 96.876.640-6, RUT 77.668.470-8, RUT 76.026.585-3, RUT 99.589.930-2, RUT 77.320.970-7, RUT 76.094.869-1, RUT 76.054.429-9, RUT 76.129.158-0, RUT 76.671.150-2, RUT 76.155.782-3, RUT 76.079.831-2, RUT 99.527.200-8, RUT 76.175.850-0, RUT 77.918.250-9, RUT 76.179.952-5, RUT 76